metadata.description:
Sugar Bae


Animated, Kawaii, Chibi, 3D, Commercial Use, Sculpture, 3D Printable, Rare, Unique NFTs


Hi! I'm the creator of BooThangs and I love making feel-good digital art! 

I like to call my special brand of chibis My Crypto Boos because they are all my little babies, my Millennials who specialize in trading Crypto Currencies, the FX, and the Stock markets. 

I believe in speaking life over people and circumstances. I also feel that millennials are the most empowered generation to date, therefore, the symbols that I have chosen to represent their soul's windows (aka their projectors onto the world) are power buttons. Each kawaii chibi crypto-boo is powerful!

Powerful enough to BE the change they want to see...within themselves, their families, within their communities, within their countries.

The sole idea behind their eyes is EMPOWERMENT!

As well all know; With great power comes great responsibility. So, as the first person to purchase this Rare, 1 of 1 NFT, Sugar-Bae, you are responsible for contributing to her backstory. (Not necessary - just really fun!)

What college did she graduate from?
Does she own any pets?
Which is her favorite activity: Crypto? Forex? or Trading Stocks?


Email me your responses: staff@cjsturgis.com

 

Each NFT comes with:

 

  • Commercial use rights of that particular character.
  • The 1 of 1 NFT itself (Animated 3D Sculpture) .MP4
  • The original HD character used in the artwork.
  • A Locked File containing the 3D Printing file (+ a base that your character stands on) for easily printing your new NFT character in real life!

 

My favorite tools for NFT creation: Adobe CC 

 

* I am not relinquishing my own rights as creator to utilize my character(s) - I am granting you - and ONLY you, the NFT owner - the commercial rights to utilize this character/character likeness/files in your own artworks for personal/commercial use.

 

Thanks for visiting. Have a great day, my loves!
